-- Saudi Saline to Spend $800 Million on Plants, Eqtisadiah Reports
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-02-13T09:02:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/saudi-saline-to-spend-800-million-on-plants-eqtisadiah-reports.html
Saudi Arabia ’s  Saline Water
Conversion Corp.  will spend 3 billion riyals ($800 million) to
renovate existing plants,  al-Eqtisadiah  reported, citing the
company’s governor Abdulrahman Al-Ibrahim.  To contact the reporter on this story:
